  • Featuring a petal-perfect corgi seed

    Welcome to the future of fashion! Our Dandelion Flying Corgi Flower Seed Tee is the perfect piece for plant-lovers, pet-lovers, and trendsetters alike! Crafted from lightweight materials, this one-of-a-kind shirt features a dandelion puff with a seed that looks like a corgi, bound for places unknown. What more could you want? Get yours while it's still sprouting!

    This tee features a cute and funny design of a corgi seed flying off a dandelion flower. It's a unique and whimsical way to show your love for these adorable dogs and nature. Whether you wear it to the park, the garden, or the dog park, you'll be sure to get compliments and smiles from everyone who sees it. This tee is made of soft and durable cotton, and comes in various colors and sizes. Order yours today and enjoy the beauty of corgis and flowers!

    Available in 12 colors and 7 different sizes, measurements are shown below. We always recommend choosing 1-2 sizes larger and comparing the measurements in the sizing chart to a tee that fits you.
